Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:56.62,main,Toki,0,0,0,,xin cứ liên lạc với tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.62,0:01:58.43,main,Miyako,0,0,0,,V-Vâng...
