Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:16.64,main,,0,0,0,,nhưng anh vẫn chưa quen được với cảm giác đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.18,main,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Cũng phải...
Comment: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.01,sign_27808_276_The_siblings_and,Sign,0,0,0,,The siblings and\Nthe academy face their \Ngreatest danger yet!!
